        <h1 class="article-title">What are BIGO strengths?</h1>
        <p class="lead" style="text-align: center;">BIGO takes advantage of the validation data generated by gene enrichment analysis tools, providing new information which helps to enclose the results and to generate new conclusions. Concretely, BIGO generates a ranking of biological terms and a network that shows the hidden relationships between different genes collections.</p>

