                <h5 style="font-weight: lighter; text-align: justify;">
                    BIGO generates a network from the biological term ranking that represents the relationship between the groups of genes based on the number of biological terms they share. 
                </h5>
                <h5 style="font-weight: bold; text-align: justify;">
                    This graph is able to show groups of genes which are well-defined and independent from each other. Moreover, those closely related groups are also interesting, in case they do not share a high proportion of their genes or, in other case, to simplify results overlapping them.
                </h5>
            </div>
